\ul\b\fs24 Version notes\ulnone\b0\fs20\par
\pard\li360 The menu option for running Mo'PaQ 2000 scripts has support for almost everything.  The /r switch may only be used with Add, and the /lf and /p switches are not used with the List command because WinMPQ does not display the list to the screen.  Scripts can be run within each other in WinMPQ.  Use the /auto parameter with the Add command to use compression auto-selection.\par
\pard\par
